#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:1629
msgid "``gc_ringidx``: the index of the ring where the self-contact occurs."
msgstr "``gc_ringidx``: de index van de ring waar het zelfcontact optreedt."

