#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:1768
msgid "``gc_errorx``: the x coordinate of the self-intersection."
msgstr "``gc_errorx``: de X-coördinaat van het zelf doorsnijden."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:1769
msgid "``gc_errory``: the y coordinate of the self-intersection."
msgstr "``gc_errory``: de Y-coördinaat van het zelf doorsnijden."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:1771
msgid ""
"``gc_segment_1``: the index of the first segment involved in the "
