#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:2050
msgid "``gc_error``: the error angle value."
msgstr "``gc_error``: de foutwaarde van de hoek."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:2051
msgid ""
"``UNIQUE_ID`` field: the unique ID of the input feature with the small "
