" bevat. :ref:`Een van <output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:2125
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:2187
msgid "**Small polygons features**"
msgstr "**Objecten Kleine polygonen**"

