msgstr ""
"Uitvoerlaag die de geometrieën van de gaten bevat. Beschikbare velden zijn "
"hetzelfde als in de uitvoer ``ERRORS``."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:2371
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:checkgeometrygap``"
msgstr "**ID algoritme**: ``native:checkgeometrygap``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:2381
msgid "Small segments"
msgstr "Korte segmenten"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:2384
msgid ""
"Calculates length of individual segments in line or polygon geometries, and "
"reports segments shorter than a minimum length as errors."
msgstr ""
"Berekent lengten van individuele segmenten in geometrieën lijn of polygoon "
"en rapporteert segmenten, die korter zijn dan een minimale lengte, als "
"fouten."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:2390
msgid ""
"Reporting errors (in red) on single line segments shorter than the given "
"threshold."
msgstr ""
"Fouten rapporteren (in rood) voor segmenten van een enkele lijn die korter "
"zijn dan de opgegeven drempelwaarde."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:2417
msgid "**Minimum segment length**"
msgstr "**Minimale lengte segment**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:2418
msgid "``MIN_SEGMENT_LENGTH``"
msgstr "``MIN_SEGMENT_LENGTH``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:2422
msgid "Minimum length of segments to be considered valid, in map units."
msgstr ""
"Minimale lengte van segmenten die als geldig moeten worden beschouwd, in "
"kaarteenheden."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:2423
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:2482
msgid "**Short segments errors**"
msgstr "**Fouten Korte segmenten**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:2428
msgid ""
"Specification of the output layer containing centroid of short segments. "
":ref:`One of <output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Specificatie van de uitvoerlaag die de zwaartepunten van de korte segmenten "
"bevat. :ref:`Een van <output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:2434
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:2497
msgid "**Short segments features**"
msgstr "**Objecten Korte segmenten**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:2441
msgid ""
"Specification of the output layer for features containing short segments. "
":ref:`One of <output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Specificatie van de uitvoerlaag voor objecten die korte segmenten bevatten. "
":ref:`Een van <output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/checkgeometry.rst:2490
msgid ""
"``gc_partidx``: the index of the feature's geometry part containing the "
